```
.cake {
  width: 200px;
  height: 150px;
  background-color: #f2c464;
  border-radius: 10px;
  position: relative;
}
.candles {
  position: absolute;
  top: -20px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.candle {
  width: 10px;
  height: 30px;
  background-color: #ffd700;
  margin: 0 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: relative;
}
.candle::before {
  content: '';
  width: 2px;
  height: 10px;
  background-color: #ffa07a;
  position: absolute;
  top: -10px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.balloons {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -50px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.balloon {
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: relative;
  margin: 0 10px;
}
.balloon.red {
  background-color: #ff69b4;
}
.balloon.blue {
  background-color: #87ceeb;
}
.balloon.green {
  background-color: #32cd32;
}
.balloon::before {
  content: '';
  width: 2px;
  height: 20px;
  background-color: #666;
  position: absolute;
  top: 30px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
```
