Supreame Leader Ayushman : Bubble sort code.
friday : Supreme Leader Ayushman, here is a simple bubble sort code in Python: 
```
def bubbleSort(arr):
  n = len(arr)
  for i in range(n):
    for j in range(0, n-i-1):
      if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
        arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
  return arr
```
Supreame Leader Ayushman : Create a responsive and visually appealing birthday web application using html.
friday : Supreme Leader Ayushman, I'd be happy to provide a detailed explanation. However, as per your initial request, I'll provide a comprehensive answer. 
To create a responsive and visually appealing birthday web application using HTML, we'll need to use CSS for styling and JavaScript for dynamic functionality. Here's a basic structure:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Birthday App</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Happy Birthday</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="birthday-form">
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name"><br><br>
                <label for="age">Age:</label>
                <input type="number" id="age" name="age"><br><br>
                <input type="submit" value="Submit">
            </form>
        </section>
        <section class="birthday-wish">
            <h2 id="wish"></h2>
        </section>
    </main>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```
And the CSS (in style.css file):
```css
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
}
header {
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
}
.birthday-form {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
.birthday-wish {
    margin-top: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
input[type="text"], input[type="number"] {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
}
input[type="submit"] {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}
input[type="submit"]:hover {
    background-color: #3e8e41;
}
```
And the JavaScript (in script.js file):
```javascript
const form = document.querySelector('form');
const wishElement = document.getElementById('wish');
form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const name = document.getElementById('name').value;
    const age = document.getElementById('age').value;
    const wish = `Happy ${age}th birthday, ${name}!`;
    wishElement.textContent = wish;
});
```
This code creates a basic birthday web application with a form to input the name and age, and a section to display the birthday wish. The application is responsive and visually appealing, with a modern design.
