friday : Supreme Leader Ayushman, here's a Python implementation of Bubble Sort:
```
def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(n-i-1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
    return arr
arr = [64, 34, 25, 12, 22, 11, 90]
